Class SensorData<T extends java.io.Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • sensor_network.SensorData<T>

    fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.SensorDataI, java.io.Serializable

    public class SensorData<T extends java.io.Serializable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.SensorDataI
    This class represents sensor data collected by a sensor node, including its node ID, sensor ID, value, and timestamp. It implements the SensorDataI interface.
